  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About the game:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As an explorer, you will come to an unknown sea areas and lost land, where many dinosaurs and other prehistoric creatures live. They are not extinct and have formed a unique ecological environment. You need to collect resources, build shelters, craft weapons, and fight against ferocious dinosaurs.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Male and female character customization system, freely customize your appearance, makeup, age, weight, and various clothing<br></li><li>Supports single player and multiplayer mode, you can survive and explore with friends<br></li><li>Wide variety of dinosaurs and prehistoric creatures, high quality model and realistic animations.<br></li><li>Make weapons to hunt dinosaurs</li></ul></p>[/*]<li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A vast open world map, based on realistic scan plant models and natural landscapes.</p></li><li>Dynamic day and night cycle system and weather changes, 3D clouds </li>[/list]",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About the game:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As an explorer, you will come to an unknown sea areas and lost land, where many dinosaurs and other prehistoric creatures live. They are not extinct and have formed a unique ecological environment. You need to collect resources, build shelters, craft weapons, and fight against ferocious dinosaurs.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Male and female character customization system, freely customize your appearance, makeup, age, weight, and various clothing<br></li><li>Supports single player and multiplayer mode, you can survive and explore with friends<br></li><li>Wide variety of dinosaurs and prehistoric creatures, high quality model and realistic animations.<br></li><li>Make weapons to hunt dinosaurs</li></ul></p>[/*]<li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A vast open world map, based on realistic scan plant models and natural landscapes.</p></li><li>Dynamic day and night cycle system and weather changes, 3D clouds </li>[/list]",
